Blackmailer
The man blackmailing Aunt Zara has set a place and time to bring the amount of money he demands.
#subobj 1
Find the designated place
You need to hang the money for the blackmailer's silence on one of the palm trees on the plantation north of town.
#subobj 2
Leave a message
Instead of leaving the money to some stranger, you could appropriate it and force him to give up the blackmail...
#subobj 3
Find the blackmailer
Now you have to wait for the blackmailer to come to the agreed place.
#subobj 4
Kill the blackmailer
To make sure he never deals with extortion again.
